Step-by-Step Setup
Step 1 – Assemble Antenna
    • Mount the V-Dipole antenna outdoors. 
    • Ensure an unobstructed sky view. 
Step 2 – Connect LNA
    • Connect antenna output to LNA input. 
    • Secure all RF connections. 
Step 3 – Connect RTL-SDR
    • Connect LNA output to RTL-SDR receiver. 
Step 4 – Connect Processing Unit
    • Plug RTL-SDR into Raspberry Pi or laptop USB port. 
Step 5 – Install Software
    • Install SDR++. 
    • Install GQRX or CubicSDR. 
    • Install Python and required libraries. 
Step 6 – Signal Monitoring
    • Launch SDR software. 
    • Configure frequency range. 
    • Observe spectrum and signal strength. 
